{"tid":839971,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚搬走嘅話屋企隻寵物點？","createTime":"2018-09-28T10:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T12:27:22.000Z","uid":145111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"065ba07081a3b28a3440f9382bab37f4ab8493e0","tid":839971,"uid":145111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"假設屋企隻嘢由細跟你地一家人大，到你結婚搬走會<br />\n留低佢陪老豆老母 定<br />\n帶埋走去新屋企<br />\n求各位巴絲分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3748d977091976376201c71669a81f965f255cfa","tid":839971,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個煩惱，丫媽都好錫佢唔捨得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea47a30b4497730a98d8ab62713ed684ab8c6a8c","tid":839971,"uid":21664,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"老豆老母鍾唔鍾意佢先 錫到lone咪留佢陪老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2b83f66862e60e299c7284e518b21f408226f2","tid":839971,"uid":14065,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"接埋老豆老母去新屋"},{"pid":"b15af9ab66a745339eb2cedb372a3191fb19250a","tid":839971,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"一定帶走，最多比老豆老母得閒過黎睇"},{"pid":"3415f3ea15bfc68c31ebf6a68cc07ac53d88eb9f","tid":839971,"uid":8818,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:34:02.000Z","msg":"留低係舊屋企啦<br />\n尤其你屋企人咁錫佢<br />\n你搬走 寵物又搬走<br />\n對於屋企人算叫做雙重打擊啦<br />\n寵物留舊屋 都算係比個理由你成日返去呀"},{"pid":"1eb366e6ba07112415b3979f10ca18a1c2e3b3d3","tid":839971,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"層樓轉佢名"},{"pid":"572d33f217ab48caecdd7c0491a55c73da506495","tid":839971,"uid":189512,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"如果隻寵物太老就唔帶，怕佢唔適應新環境會影響情緒易有病。"},{"pid":"51238f3f12f549e1da6f40aa17a1be0959997921","tid":839971,"uid":81793,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"黎緊會有小朋友<br />\n要未來老爺奶奶幫手湊所以要同佢地住<br />\n佢地有鼻敏感無可能帶到狗狗過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同男朋友嘈過幾次 佢話你放假咪返屋企睇狗<br />\n屌我而家係唔想同佢分開住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話咩為左屋企 你係要接受架喇<br />\n我隻狗都係我屋企人黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我直頭有時覺得係咪唔應該結婚<br />\n我覺得我比人控制左我唔會開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人可以話我知點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41374ece1962c2496c2d84a05ca753135f0654f","tid":839971,"uid":3093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"留返佢同老豆老母一齊啦<br />\n<br />\n一來你另一半又唔知鐘唔鐘意養<br />\n二來有隻動物比兩老寄托下都好<br />\n仲有你要計下你可以用黎照顧隻動物嘅時間會唔會比兩老少？<br />\n<br />\n除非你完全唔放心佢地照顧/佢地唔鐘意咁你就要帶佢走啦"},{"pid":"14c19b610a99df1977fc5c558055469d7716ad94","tid":839971,"uid":145111,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"其實我成日都諗呢個問題但老母話分分鐘隻嘢死我都未結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓仔呀貓仔點解你唔識分身術<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/191231_285536799c715b2d6fb69a760fa0f921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F191231_285536799c715b2d6fb69a760fa0f921.jpg&h=5c2af9d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5953eba06140d97819e6ce40f4331cae4fc73c7","tid":839971,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"諗呢樣諗個樣 最後尾都係覺得自己係主人要決定佢既生死<br />\n<br />\n邊個照顧開咪跟邊個<br />\n如果大家都差唔多既<br />\n你自己搬走憑乜野想帶埋人地走"},{"pid":"5f5dff23dc95dba0378ace9d4b1f7820b5b805db","tid":839971,"uid":69939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:27:22.000Z","msg":"我都煩緊呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就快結婚將會搬走 女朋友唔鐘意寵物<br />\n<br />\n隻寵物9成時間我照顧 <br />\n平時屋企人唔多理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好錫隻寵物 雖然唔係我帶佢番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果搬走 我會好唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}